WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.740 --> 00:00:02.450
Your body has a silent guardian,

1
00:00:02.930 --> 00:00:04.969
working every second without rest.

2
00:00:05.389 --> 00:00:08.520
The lymphatic system is both your first and last line of defense,

3
00:00:09.069 --> 00:00:12.010
protecting balance within and restoring order when threats appear.

4
00:00:12.449 --> 00:00:15.210
At the core of this protection is your immune system.

5
00:00:15.590 --> 00:00:17.569
Its role is simple yet powerful,

6
00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:20.909
to defend your body from external invaders like microbes,

7
00:00:21.069 --> 00:00:21.629
toxins,

8
00:00:21.670 --> 00:00:23.090
and harmful chemicals.

9
00:00:23.389 --> 00:00:24.020
To do this,

10
00:00:24.110 --> 00:00:26.649
the immune system performs a remarkable task.

11
00:00:27.030 --> 00:00:28.569
It knows what belongs to you

12
00:00:28.989 --> 00:00:29.909
and what does not.

13
00:00:30.420 --> 00:00:32.880
This ability to recognize self from non-self

14
00:00:33.259 --> 00:00:34.520
is what keeps you alive.

15
00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.200
Think of your immune system as an army,

16
00:00:37.580 --> 00:00:38.220
always alert,

17
00:00:38.380 --> 00:00:39.319
always prepared.

18
00:00:39.779 --> 00:00:41.720
But even the strongest army needs training.

19
00:00:42.220 --> 00:00:43.459
Soldiers require fuel,

20
00:00:43.619 --> 00:00:44.099
discipline,

21
00:00:44.259 --> 00:00:44.500
rest,

22
00:00:44.540 --> 00:00:45.560
and conditioning

23
00:00:46.020 --> 00:00:47.240
to remain battle ready.

24
00:00:47.659 --> 00:00:49.279
Your immune cells are no different.

25
00:00:49.819 --> 00:00:51.220
They depend on proper nourishment,

26
00:00:51.330 --> 00:00:51.799
hydration,

27
00:00:52.139 --> 00:00:52.919
deep sleep,

28
00:00:53.340 --> 00:00:55.720
and healthy movement to function at their peak.

29
00:00:56.139 --> 00:00:57.259
Without these foundations,

30
00:00:57.380 --> 00:00:58.380
defenses weaken.

31
00:00:58.889 --> 00:01:01.549
No matter how powerful the system is designed to be,

32
00:01:02.009 --> 00:01:03.869
your immune system fights everything,

33
00:01:04.330 --> 00:01:06.080
from common colds and fevers,

34
00:01:06.410 --> 00:01:08.750
to long-term complex diseases like cancer.

35
00:01:09.169 --> 00:01:09.959
Train it well,

36
00:01:10.410 --> 00:01:11.349
support it daily,

37
00:01:11.769 --> 00:01:13.830
and when your body needs protection the most,

38
00:01:14.250 --> 00:01:16.720
your immune system will stand and fight for you.